resources.string:
"Njengomsizi efonini yakho, iGemini ingakusiza ukuthi ubhale amanothi okubonga, uhlele imicimbi, ufunde izinto ezintsha, usethe ama-alamu, wenze amakholi, nokuningi.
Ngemva kokusetha ifoni yakho, mane ucindezele futhi ubambe inkinobho yamandla ukuze uqalise ngeGemini."
IGemini, ingokusiza i-AI yakho okwakhelwe ngaphakathi
Qinisekisa ukuthi wonke umuntu ufakiwe esithombeni seqembu
Sesha, londoloza, futhi uhlele ulwazi, wenze izinto zenzeke, futhi uqale ngobuciko
